        "description": "(This is the demo version of Goal Poacher VR)\n\nBecome a pro striker who scores headers from corner kicks and free-kicks in a football simulator.\n\n# REAL-LIFE GOAL SCORING SCENARIO\nWe put together over many levels inspired by real-life goals that will test your header skills. \n\n\n# CHALLENGING DEFENDERS AI\n\n\nThe defenders and goalkeepers in this game will try their best to stop you from scoring. You have to quickly assert their positions and decide where to put the ball to maximize scoring chance (as in real life).\n\n# REALISTIC BALL HEADING PHYSICS\nWe developed our projectile physics to correctly simulate the ball projectile with drag, Magnus effect, and collision check with your head to ensure a realistic heading experience.\n\n\n\n# NEVER PLAYED FOOTBALL IRL? WE GOT YOU COVERED!\n\nWe have slow-motion options so heading becomes easy for new players! We have also prepared a tutorial section to teach you the technique in our training facility!\n\n\n\n\n# REALISTIC GOAL-NET PHYSICS\n\n\n \n\n\n\n",
